;font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char;line-height:23.0000pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\r\nbackground:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">地址：盐城市钱江财富广场</font><font face=\"宋体\">A座4楼</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char;line-height:23.0000pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\r\nbackground:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">联系人：吴女士</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;mso-layout-grid-align:none;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char;line-height:23.0000pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;\r\nbackground:rgb(255,255,255);\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;color:rgb(0,0,0);\r\nfont-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">电话：</font><font face=\"宋体\">0515-89803</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">566 &nbsp;15950298580</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2988','3813','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院主院区碎石机房装修项目已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：一、招标人名称：盐城市第一人民医院 二、招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司','172.16.1.2','172.16.1.2','1668043624','<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院主院区碎石机房装修项目已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">一、招标人名称：</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">第一人民医院<span>&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">二、招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">三、项目概况：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程名称：盐城市第一人民医院主院区碎石机房装修项目。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路<span>66</span>号）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、招标规模：工程造价约<span>7.4</span>万元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、招标范围及内容：盐城市第一人民医院主院区碎石机房装修项目的施工，具体内容详见招标人提供的图纸及工程量清单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工期要求：<span>20</span>日历天，具体开工日期以招标人的通知为准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、质量标准：符合国家“合格”标准，质保期<span>2</span>年。必须达到国家关于《放射性同位素与射线装置安全和防护条例》、《电离辐射防护与辐射源安全基本标准》、《医用<span>X</span>射线诊断卫生防护标准》、《医用<span>X</span>射线诊断卫生防护监测规范》《医用电子加速器卫防护标准》《临床核医学放射卫生防护标准》等的辐射防护法律法规的要求。并保证通过卫生、环保部门预评价、防护检测及竣工验收等环节。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">四、投标人资格要求：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:22.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人必须是在中国境内注册，具有独立完成本项目所有工作的能力的独立法人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:22.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、项目负责人资格类别和等级：项目经理须是投标人本单位在职职工且非法定代表人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。<span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人须确保主要设备、材料（防辐射材料、防辐射门窗等）应具有卫生行政主管部门颁发的有效的《放射防护器材检测报告》。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标申请人须保证委托代理人、项目负责人均为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续<span>6</span>个月均已在本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如开标日期为<span>2020</span>年<span>7</span>月的某一天，则投标单位需保证以上人员<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月养老保险均在本单位缴纳）。投标时无须提供证明材料，如有质疑或招标人要求，再按要求提供相关证明材料。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">五、招标文件获取：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">请符合要求的潜在投标人于</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">16</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">日（每日上午</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时至</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">00</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时，下午</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">14</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时至</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">18</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">00</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时）携带单位介绍信原件（或授权委托书原件，注明联系人电话及邮箱）至江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司（</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市紫薇广场<span>C</span>区<span>7</span>楼</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">）报名并领取招标文件（联系人：周会计，联系电话：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">0515-88200706</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">18705110288</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">）</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">，逾期不再受理。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">六、投标保证金</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">本项目投标保证金为人民币<span>1500</span>元，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">七、本项目资格审查办法采用<b>资格后审</b>；评标办法采用<b>综合评估法</b>，具体详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">八、本项目严禁挂靠，一经核实挂靠，将被取消投标、中标资格，并按相关规定进行处罚，直至建议有关部门吊销资质证书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">九、联系方式</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">地<span>&nbsp; </span>址<span style=\"color:black\">：人民南路<span>66</span>号</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">联系人：沈剑</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">电<span>&nbsp; </span>话：<span>18662081713</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">地<span>&nbsp; </span>址：盐城市紫薇广场<span>C</span>区<span>7</span>楼<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">联系人：尤鸿望、张旭良<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">电<span>&nbsp; </span>话：<span>0515-88200316</span>、<span>13515130964</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:1.15;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:22.0pt\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2989','3814','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院放射诊疗设备年度检测服务项目已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：一、招标人名称：盐城市第一人民医院 二、招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价咨询有','172.16.1.2','172.16.1.2','1668043674','<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院放射诊疗设备年度检测服务项目已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">一、招标人名称：</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">第一人民医院<span>&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">二、招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">三、项目概况：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程名称：盐城市第一人民医院放射诊疗设备年度检测服务项目。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程地点：盐城市第一人民医院南区、北区、五官科医院、紫薇广场门诊及儿童医院。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、本项目最高限价：<span>17</span>万元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:25.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、招标范围及内容：（<span>1</span>）按甲方提供的设备清单对放射诊疗设备和场所（包括卫生和环保）进行质量控制检测和放射工作场所职业病危害因素检测；（<span>2</span>）职业病危害相关技术咨询；（<span>3</span>）其他事项。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、服务质量：符合国家规范及行业标准，形成书面报告，并通过卫生、环保等监管部门的验收，并取得相关证书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:19.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、服务期：<span>1 </span>年。服务期满，经招标人考核合格、服务符合要求后，可续签下一年合同，续签不超过两次。如续签，设备性能检测以医院实际设备数为准，按实结算，具体开始日期以招标人的书面通知为准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">四、投标人资格要求：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人是在中华人民共和国境内登记注册的具有独立法人资格的单位，能独立承担民事责任；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人须具有职业卫生（放射卫生）技术服务机构甲级资质；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人须具备与投标检测设备相符合的<span>CMA</span>计量认证内容并提供证书及附件；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人资质需经省级及以上卫生主管部门和环保主管部门认可。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、本项目招标人不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。<span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标申请人须保证委托代理人、项目负责人均为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续<span>6</span>个月均已在本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如开标日期为<span>2020</span>年<span>7</span>月的某一天，则投标单位需保证以上人员<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月养老保险均在本单位缴纳）。投标时无须提供证明材料，如有质疑或招标人要求，再按要求提供相关证明材料。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">五、竞争性谈判文件获取：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">请符合要求的潜在投标人于</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">16</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">日（每日上午</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时至</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">00</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时，下午</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">14</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时至</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">18</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">00</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时）携带单位介绍信原件（或授权委托书原件，注明联系人电话及邮箱）至江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司（</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市紫薇广场<span>C</span>区<span>7</span>楼</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">）报名并领取竞争性谈判文件（联系人：周会计，联系电话：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">0515-88200706</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">18705110288</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">）</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">，逾期不再受理。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">六、投标保证金</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">本项目投标保证金为人民币<span>2000</span>元，具体详见竞争性谈判文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">七、本项目资格审查办法采用<b>资格后审</b>；评标办法采用<b>竞争性谈判方式</b>，具体详见谈判文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">八、本项目严禁挂靠，一经核实挂靠，将被取消投标、中标资格，并按相关规定进行处罚，直至建议有关部门吊销资质证书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">九、联系方式</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">地<span>&nbsp; </span>址：人民南路<span>66</span>号</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">联系人：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">周先生</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">电<span>&nbsp; </span>话：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">18932281211</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">地<span>&nbsp; </span>址：盐城市紫薇广场<span>C</span>区<span>7</span>楼<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">联系人：张先生<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">电<span>&nbsp; </span>话：<span>0515-88200316</span>、<span>13515130964</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2990','3815','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院工作人员个人剂量监测服务项目已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：一、招标人名称：盐城市第一人民医院 二、招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价咨询有','172.16.1.2','172.16.1.2','1668043715','<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院工作人员个人剂量监测服务项目已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">一、招标人名称：</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">第一人民医院<span>&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">二、招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">三、项目概况：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程名称：盐城市第一人民医院工作人员个人剂量监测服务项目。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程地点：</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:black\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、本项目最高限价：<span>\r\n4.5</span>万元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、招标范围及内容：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">负责院方放射工作人员的职业外照射个人剂量监测服务。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、服务期限：<span>1</span>年（每季度进行一次监测，<span>1</span>年<span>4</span>次。）</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">服务期满，经招标人考核合格、服务符合要求后，可续签下一年合同，续签不超过两次。个人剂量监测服务</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">以医院实际工作人数为准，按实结算，</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">具体开始日期以招标人的书面通知为准</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、质量标准：个人剂量计更换时间为每季度一次，为保证个人剂量监测数据的真实性、准确性、有效性，中标人该及时通知招标人更换新剂量计。每个周期监测数据出一次报告。监测时出现异常剂量应及时向招标人反馈信息。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:26.25pt;line-height:21.0pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">、工作人员数量：约<span>250</span>人<span>/</span>年。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">四、投标人资格要求：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人是在中华人民共和国境内登记注册的具有独立法人资格的单位，能独立承担民事责任，且具有检验检测机构资质认定证书（<span>CMA</span>）和放射卫生技术服务机构资质证书，证书附表中包含相关个人剂量检测能力、放射诊疗设备性能及防护检测能力、预控评技术服务能力。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。<span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标申请人须保证委托代理人、项目负责人均为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续<span>6</span>个月均已在本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如开标日期为<span>2020</span>年<span>7</span>月的某一天，则投标单位需保证以上人员<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月养老保险均在本单位缴纳）。投标时无须提供证明材料，如有质疑或招标人要求，再按要求提供相关证明材料。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">五、竞争性谈判文件获取：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">请符合要求的潜在投标人于</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">16</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">日（每日上午</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时至</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">00</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时，下午</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">14</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时至</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">18</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">00</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时）携带单位介绍信原件（或授权委托书原件，注明联系人电话及邮箱）至江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司（</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市紫薇广场<span>C</span>区<span>7</span>楼</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">）报名并领取竞争性谈判文件（联系人：周会计，联系电话：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">0515-88200706</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">18705110288</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">）</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">，逾期不再受理。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">六、投标保证金</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">本项目投标保证金为人民币<span>900</span>元，具体详见竞争性谈判文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">七、本项目资格审查办法采用<b>资格后审</b>；评标办法采用<b>竞争性谈判方式</b>，具体详见谈判文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">八、本项目严禁挂靠，一经核实挂靠，将被取消投标、中标资格，并按相关规定进行处罚，直至建议有关部门吊销资质证书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">九、联系方式</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">地<span>&nbsp; </span>址：人民南路<span>66</span>号</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">联系人：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">周先生</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">电<span>&nbsp; </span>话：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">18932281211</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">地<span>&nbsp; </span>址：盐城市紫薇广场<span>C</span>区<span>7</span>楼<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">联系人：张先生<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">电<span>&nbsp; </span>话：<span>0515-88200316</span>、<span>13515130964</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';line-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">&nbsp;</span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2991','3816','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院放射诊疗设备稳定性检测服务项目已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：一、招标人名称：盐城市第一人民医院 二、招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价咨询','172.16.1.2','172.16.1.2','1668043775','<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院放射诊疗设备稳定性检测服务项目已具备招标条件，项目所需资金来源为自筹资金并已落实。现通过公开招标方式邀请潜在投标人参加本项目的投标报名。现就有关事项公告如下：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">一、招标人名称：</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">第一人民医院<span>&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:22.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">二、招标代理机构：江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">三、项目概况：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程名称：盐城市第一人民医院放射诊疗设备稳定性检测服务项目。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程地点：</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、本项目最高限价：<span>9.7</span>万元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4</span>、招标范围及内容：<span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院放射诊疗设备稳定性检测服务，包括但不限于：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char\">（<span style=\"font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'\">1</span>）按甲方提供的设备清单对放射诊疗设备稳定性检测服务；</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';text-indent:21.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char\">（<span style=\"font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'\">2</span>）对放射诊疗设备进行稳定性检测；采购人保留对上述暂定招标内容适当调整的权利。具体采购内容详见项目需求。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5</span>、服务质量：符合国家规范及行业标准，形成书面报告，并通过卫生、环保等监管部门的验收，并取得相关证书。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">、服务期：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\'\">1 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">年。服务期满，经招标人考核合格、服务符合要求后，可续签下一年合同，续签不超过两次。</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">如续签，设备稳定性检测以医院实际设备数为准，按实结算，</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">具体开始日</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">期以招标人的书面通知为准</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">四、投标人资格要求：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人是在中华人民共和国境内登记注册的具有独立法人资格的单位，能独立承担民事责任；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人须具有职业卫生（放射卫生）技术服务机构甲级资质；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人须具备与投标检测设备相符合的<span>CMA</span>计量认证内容并提供证书及附件；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人资质需经省级及以上卫生主管部门和环保主管部门认可。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、本项目招标人不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。<span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标申请人须保证委托代理人、项目负责人均为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续<span>6</span>个月均已在本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如开标日期为<span>2020</span>年<span>7</span>月的某一天，则投标单位需保证以上人员<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月养老保险均在本单位缴纳）。投标时无须提供证明材料，如有质疑或招标人要求，再按要求提供相关证明材料。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">五、竞争性谈判文件获取：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">请符合要求的潜在投标人于</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">日至</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">16</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">日（每日上午</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时至</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">00</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时，下午</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">14</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时至</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">18</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">00</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">时）携带单位介绍信原件（或授权委托书原件，注明联系人电话及邮箱）至江苏双清工程造价咨询有限公司（</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市紫薇广场<span>C</span>区<span>7</span>楼</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">）报名并领取竞争性谈判文件（联系人：周会计，联系电话：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">0515-88200706</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">18705110288</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">）</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">，逾期不再受理。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">六、投标保证金</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">本项目投标保证金为人民币<span>2000</span>元，具体详见竞争性谈判文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">七、本项目资格审查办法采用<b>资格后审</b>；评标办法采用<b>竞争性谈判方式</b>，具体详见谈判文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">八、本项目严禁挂靠，一经核实挂靠，将被取消投标、中标资格，并按相关规定进行处罚，直至建议有关部门吊销资质证书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'嫤疓B2312\',\'serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">九、联系方式</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0p